<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>This is a reminder that the issue reported by <%= @data["agent_name"] %> via email remains unresolved in our system. We urge you to address this matter promptly.</p>
    <p>If the issue has been resolved but not yet marked as such, please use the button below to update the status.</p>
    <div>
        <% @ticket_id.each_with_index do |id, index|%>
        <p>subject:<%= @subject[index]%></p>
        <p>On: <%= @assigned_date[index] %></p>
        <a href="https://ee9c-49-37-8-255.ngrok-free.app/tickets/issue?ticketId=#{id}&agent_id=#{@agent_id}&assignee_name=#{@assignee_name}">Issue Solved</a>
        <% end %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>